<!-- Game Cheats Sectional -->

<table border="0" width="100%" id="table16" cellpadding="0">
	<tr>
		<td style="font-family: Trebuchet MS; font-size: 8pt; color: #FFFFFF; font-weight: bold; text-align: left; background-color: #333333; border-left: 2px solid #000000; border-right: 2px solid #FFFFFF; border-top: 2px solid #000000; border-bottom: 2px solid #FFFFFF">
          		<br><u><i><font color="#FFFF00">MISC CODES:</font></i></u><br>
			&nbsp; Ammo refill -
                  &nbsp; <font color="#00FF00">In foot mode do a backflip by pressing Square + L2. During the backflip press Right + X + Circle</font>&nbsp;
			<br>&nbsp; Fart Noises -
                  &nbsp; <font color="#00FF00">At the main menu select Load Game and press L1 + L2 + R1 + R2</font>&nbsp;
			<br>&nbsp; Full Health -
                  &nbsp; <font color="#00FF00">While playing do a backflip by pressing Square + L2. While in the air press Down + X + R2</font>&nbsp;
			<br>&nbsp; Full Inventory -
                  &nbsp; <font color="#00FF00">Enter map mode and press left until the arrow is pointing at you. Press Start to rotate into the standard view. During the rotation press L1 + Square + X + Circle</font>&nbsp;
			<br>&nbsp; Level Select -
                  &nbsp; <font color="#00FF00">At the main menu hold L1 + L2 + R1 + R2 + Up, then release and start a new game. At the difficulty level screen hold L1 + L2 + R1 + R2 + Down</font>&nbsp;
			<br>&nbsp; Watch Final Sequence -
                  &nbsp; <font color="#00FF00">Highlight load game on the main menu, hold Right and press Circle. Release Right and press Triangle + Left + Square, then Triangle once more</font>&nbsp;<br><br>
	 </tr>
	</table>
       	</td>

     </tr>
</table>

